# OPENAI_API_KEY: Required by the Cloudflare Pages function (/api/generate-plan).
#
# Production:  Set via the Cloudflare Dashboard → Pages → Settings → Environment Variables
# Local dev:   Create a .env file in the project root with your key, then run
#              `npm run dev:wrangler` so Wrangler picks it up.
#
# This key is NEVER sent to the browser — it stays server-side.
OPENAI_API_KEY=""
